Download deployment data from Google drive to the shared CMAR server

ss_download_data.Rd

Download deployment data from Google drive to the shared CMAR server

Usage

ss_download_data(path, station, depl_date)

Arguments

path

File path to the deployment folder on the CMAR server (as created by ss_set_up_folders()).

station

Station name. Should match the name of a folder on the CMAR Google drive, in CMAR - Coastal Monitoring Program/CMP Station Data

depl_date

Deployment date (character string). Should be in the name of one of the deployment folders.

Value

Downloads files from Google drive to the corresponding folder on the CMAR server.
